message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product for $95. I believe this price reflects the value it holds for both of us.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of your product. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $85.
Thank you for your counteroffer, Bob. I understand your valuation of the product. Let me make a proposal of $90 for the product. I hope this aligns better with your expectations.
I appreciate your effort, Alice. Considering my budget, I would like to propose a counteroffer of $82 for the product.

Thank you for your latest proposal, Bob. I appreciate your consideration. I would like to counter with an offer of $88 for the product. I believe this brings us closer to a mutually beneficial agreement.
